<div class="flex flex-col lg:ml-10 lg:mt-8">
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Penilaian Kriteria</h1>
  <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-6">
    Pada penilaian kriteria, kandidat yang telah terpilih pada tahap voting akan dinilai berdasarkan 21 kriteria. Setiap kriteria akan diberikan penilaian dengan skala:
    <br />
    1 (Sangat Tidak Sesuai), 2 (Tidak Sesuai), 3 (Sesuai), 4 (Sangat Sesuai).
  </p>
  <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-6">
    Penilaian ini bertujuan untuk memberikan evaluasi yang objektif dalam menentukan hasil akhir sesuai dengan kriteria yang telah ditetapkan.
  </p>

  <!-- Form Penilaian -->
  <form class="mt-8 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-300 shadow-sm p-6 space-y-6 overflow-auto" style="max-height: 60vh;">
    <!-- Tabel Penilaian -->
    <table class="table-auto w-full text-left border-collapse">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b-2 border-gray-300">Kategori</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b-2 border-gray-300">Indikator</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b-2 border-gray-300">Frizqya Dela Pratiwi</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b-2 border-gray-300">Annisa Nurul Hakim</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-2 border-b-2 border-gray-300">Muhammad Raihan Alghifari</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each rows as |row index|}}
        <tr>
          <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200">{{row.category}}</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200">{{row.indicator}}</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200">
            <ol class="space-y-1">
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-frizqya" value="1" /> 1</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-frizqya" value="2" /> 2</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-frizqya" value="3" /> 3</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-frizqya" value="4" /> 4</label></li>
            </ol>
          </td>
          <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200">
            <ol class="space-y-1">
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-annisa" value="1" /> 1</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-annisa" value="2" /> 2</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-annisa" value="3" /> 3</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-annisa" value="4" /> 4</label></li>
            </ol>
          </td>
          <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-gray-200">
            <ol class="space-y-1">
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-muhammad" value="1" /> 1</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-muhammad" value="2" /> 2</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-muhammad" value="3" /> 3</label></li>
              <li><label><input type="radio" name="criteria-{{index}}-muhammad" value="4" /> 4</label></li>
            </ol>
          </td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- Button Simpan -->
    <button
  type="button"
  onclick="window.location.href='/thank-you'"
  class="mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-green-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
>
  Simpan Penilaian
</button>

  </form>
</div>
